    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Method of hand sewing a text block in which two gatherings are sewn together by a single length of thread; the thread passes between them at alternate sewing stations.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
